uk.ac.ebi.masscascade.utilities.range

Class ExtendableRange

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ebi.masscascade.utilities.range.ExtendableRange
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Range>, Range
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SimpleRange, ToleranceRange

    public class ExtendableRange
extends java.lang.Object
implements Range, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Range>
    Class implementing a data range that can be extended on the fly. The default comparison behaviour uses the lower bound of the range only.
    See Also:
